    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "These golems are crafted from abysium, the blue-green glowing starmetal also known as feverstone. They are dangerous not only for their strength and ferocity, but also because of the radiation they emit at all times. Some believe that abysium\u2014and the golems made of it\u2014are connected to the Abyss, the nightmarish home of all demonkind."
        }
